4️⃣ Responsiveness
Use CSS Media Queries to ensure responsiveness for tablets and mobiles.

@media (max-width: 768px) {
   nav ul {
       flex-direction: column;
   }

   .hero-section h1 {
       font-size: 2rem;
   }

   .service-card {
       margin-bottom: 2rem;
   }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
   header, #about, #services, #contact {
       padding: 2rem 1rem;
   }
}
